headline: Jacobs to Manage Infrastructure Development Program to Support Regional Growth in El Paso, Texas
summary: Jacobs (NYSE: J) has been selected by El Paso Water to provide program management and owner's representative services for its Utility Infrastructure Development Program near El Paso International Airport and Fort Bliss, one of the largest military installations in the U.S.
